strings: <voice_0x010011A3><se_high>Install on PC: i believe they are correct.
<voice_0x010011A4><se_def>Economy: You know, I wasn't expecting this to happen until we met him.
<voice_0x010011A5><se_def>Economy: Do we both carry on with my father's work? Who can tell
<voice_0x010011A6><se_def>Economy: Looking back, I can't believe how jealous we were that we had different heirs.
<voice_0x010011A7><se_def>Economy: It's incredible how people can change over time.
<voice_0x010011A8><se_high>Install on PC: Look here, my brother.
<voice_0x010011A9><se_high>Install on PC: I'm afraid to talk about "successors".
<voice_0x010011AA><se_def>Economy: Don't worry. I'm not suggesting anything. Let's go. It's going to rain!
<voice_0x010011AB><se_high>Install on PC: I swear to Casey. My family is going traveling.
<voice_0x010011AC><se_high>Install on PC: we respect our father
<voice_0x010011AD><se_high>Install on PC: Now that we work together, the Golding family can thrive more than ever. Compliance!
